1
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:29,080
Brushing your teeth?

2
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:31,520
Lu Jingheng,

3
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,080
please behave yourself.

4
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,479
Shen Zhixia,

5
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:36,720
you were not like this when you first met me.

6
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:37,520
I...

7
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:41,180
Why have you been avoiding me?

8
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,400
Is it because that night at the beach,

9
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,660
I didn't do well enough

10
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,000
and you were not satisfied?

11
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,400
No, I was very satisfied.

12
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:51,800
Then what exactly are you worried about?

13
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,130
What are your concerns?

14
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,200
I...

15
00:01:58,160 --> 00:02:00,360
How do you expect me to explain it to you?

16
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:02,840
That I don't belong to this world,

17
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:06,800
and I might disappear tomorrow?

18
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,840
I was just concerned

19
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:11,760
that what happened that night was too sudden.

20
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,760
I needed time.

21
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,520
Really?

22
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,360
Have you thought it through now,

23
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:29,480
or do you need me to wait a little longer?

24
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,880
I passed by the flower market today,

25
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:41,440
saw a pot of jasmine and thought of you.

26
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:44,280
I remember every time I went to your house,

27
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:47,160
the scent of your jasmine filled the air,

28
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,680
always making me feel at ease.

29
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:54,880
I really miss you.

30
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:58,040
If I can escape all this in the future,

31
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:01,560
I'd like to have a big garden

32
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,240
full of jasmine.

33
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:06,120
It would be like you're always with me.

34
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:10,160
Who on earth is this J?

35
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,440
Jasmine.

36
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:22,320
Don't you dislike rose pastries?

37
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,020
Did you change your taste?

38
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:26,440
Miss Wen knows me very well.

39
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:28,880
What do you think?

40
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,480
Wen Shuyi.

41
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:43,159
Executive Vice President and Head of Greater China Business,

42
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:45,490
a milestone built by a Global 500 company.

43
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,440
Jasmine.

44
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:55,520
Could the person who corresponded with the original owner be Wen Shuyi?

45
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,080
I wrote all of these to you.

46
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,810
Why did you return them all?

47
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,480
Didn't Miss Shen pretend not to remember?

48
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,040
Why mention this now?

49
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,920
It really is you.

50
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,980
Why are you treating me like this?

51
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:27,300
Why are you helping Su Manyun harm me?

52
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,400
Shen Zhixia.

53
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,659
Do you still remember?

54
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,700
Your dad had a bad reputation.

55
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,320
In this circle,

56
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,130
no one wanted to be your friend.

57
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,280
So you clung to me,

58
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,700
writing me letters every day,

59
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:48,040
making me your only friend.

60
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,880
You wrote about your dad's incompetence in your letters,

61
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,540
and your mom's helplessness.

62
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:01,040
Then you used

63
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,960
an almost pathetic way

64
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,480
to make me your only friend.

65
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,520
I also told you.

66
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:21,840
I am in love with my brother, Wen Zhuocheng.

67
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:23,640
And then?

68
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:26,480
My father found out about it immediately.

69
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:28,000
He forced me to marry someone else,

70
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,160
and made me leave.

71
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,560
You were the only one who knew about this.

72
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,090
Who else could it be but you?

73
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,700
The original host really leaked her secret.

74
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:36,880
Why did she do it?

75
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:42,380
All these years, I've been married to a man I don't love.

76
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:45,360
I was all alone abroad.

77
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,520
When I saw you for the first time...

78
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:51,650
You actually pretended not to know me.

79
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,360
This is my friend,

80
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,840
Miss Wen Shuyi.

81
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,680
Miss Wen is so beautiful.

82
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,159
Nice to meet you.

83
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,780
I will take everything away from you.

84
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:08,160
I want you to taste betrayal.

85
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,760
For everything I've done to you,

86
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,640
I have no regrets.

87
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,280
Get out.

88
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:19,640
I feel sick just looking at your face.

89
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,400
Get out.

90
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,800
Brother.

91
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:01,480
Brother.

92
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,280
Brother.

93
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,480
Shuyi.

94
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,160
Brother.

95
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,640
I miss you.

96
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,360
Shuyi.

97
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,160
Let go.

98
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,320
You are drunk.

99
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:36,360
Brother.

100
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,640
Only when I'm drunk

101
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,100
dare I come to find you.

102
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:47,840
Stop messing around.

103
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,680
It's too late.

104
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,240
I'll take you back.

105
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,200
What are you hiding from?

106
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,920
Stop this.

107
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,480
You can't let this mistake continue.

108
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:30,280
When I sent you abroad back then,

109
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:33,240
I thought a greater distance

110
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:36,040
would end this mistake.

111
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:37,570
What did you say?

112
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,200
Back then,

113
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:46,420
you always found excuses to be close to me

114
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:48,960
and always looked at me smiling.

115
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,610
That closeness went beyond siblings;

116
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,900
it was no longer a sister's reliance.

117
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:00,680
How could I not know what you were thinking?

118
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:05,080
I thought about it over and over,

119
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:07,020
how I should persuade you,

120
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:09,170
and how to avoid you.

121
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,330
In the end, it was me.

122
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:16,330
I was the one who told Uncle.

123
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,120
I thought that was the only way

124
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:21,450
to stop you from going down the wrong path.

125
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,800
I thought sending you abroad

126
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,440
would end your obsession.

127
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,480
But I really didn't know

128
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:33,780
Uncle arranged a marriage for you

129
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,040
and forced you to marry.

130
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,040
I also didn't know

131
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:38,300
you were unhappy after getting married.

132
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,820
I'm sorry for failing you.

133
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:46,480
I also told you

134
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:49,560
that I loved my brother, Wen Zhuocheng.

135
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,160
And then?

136
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:54,000
My dad immediately found out about this,

137
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,520
forced me to marry someone else,

138
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:56,780
and forced me to leave.

139
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,080
Only you knew this secret.

140
00:10:58,080 --> 00:11:00,140
If it wasn't you, who else could it be?

141
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,280
Are you saying...

142
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,250
For all these years,

143
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,200
I've hated the wrong person?

144
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,280
You knew how I felt about you,

145
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:20,280
yet you told my dad to send me abroad.

146
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:25,760
I thought it would only be a temporary separation.

147
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:28,120
I really didn't know your dad was forcing you to get married.

148
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:28,840
If I had known...

149
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,170
So what if you had known?

150
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:33,170
Would you have been willing to make mistakes with me?

151
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:38,720
You just wanted to be

152
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,840
the righteous and kind good brother.

153
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,320
Shuyi.

154
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,320
Don't touch me.

155
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:40,130
I sent you abroad back then,

156
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:43,290
thinking that the distance

157
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:46,120
would end this mistake.

158
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,440
I thought sending you abroad

159
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,040
would end your obsession.

160
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,760
But I really didn't know

161
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,120
that Uncle arranged a marriage for you

162
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,400
and forced you to marry.

163
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,320
I didn't know

164
00:12:57,360 --> 00:13:00,290
that you were unhappy after getting married either.

165
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:02,720
Wen Shuyi.

166
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,000
Wen Shuyi.

167
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,160
Are you saying

168
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:12,500
that I've been hating the wrong person all these years?

169
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,520
I also told you

170
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:17,600
that I loved my brother, Wen Zhuocheng.

171
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:19,680
And then?

172
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:22,480
My dad found out about it immediately

173
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:24,000
and forced me to marry someone else.

174
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,260
And forced me to leave.

175
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:26,560
Only you knew this secret.

176
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:28,090
Who else could it be but you?

177
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:34,040
Lu Jingheng, I want to marry you.

178
00:13:34,040 --> 00:13:35,100
Let's get married.

179
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:37,680
Jingheng, please help me.

180
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:39,260
Even if it's just for show.

181
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,360
If you propose,

182
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,720
my family will definitely agree.

183
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:43,200
You want me to propose to you?

184
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,080
I can't do that.

